	   <tr><td colspan=2>Warriors already get triple at 60.&nbsp;&nbsp;Now monks will as well.<br><br>Epic is 9/16, and that's when you're fighting empty handed - so yes you have to leave weapon slots open.  However, there is a right-click 40% haste that you can use with weapons.  Your damage delay with weapons will be the weapons' damage delay, subject to haste.  Of course the weapons need to be better than 9/16 to make it worthwhile.<br><br>&nbsp;<br>Keyeluke<br>Member of Tenacity - Druzzil Ro<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=27415" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=27415</a></td></tr>
